text: ke’inezīya mets’iḥāfini keteset’uti sewochi inezīyani be’ālahina bemech’ereshawi k’eni yemayaminutini፣ ālahina melikitenyawi irimi yaderegutinimi irimi yemayaderigutinina iwinetenyawinimi hayimanoti yemayik’ebelutini inerisu yetewaredu ẖonewi gibirini be’ijochachewi isikemīset’u diresi tewaguwachewi፡፡
